io.elegie.luchess.core.indexing.workflow

Interface GameIndexer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LuceneGameIndexer

    public interface GameIndexer

    This interface is used by the framework to notify implementations that a new game has been parsed, so that they include it into their index.

    It is supposed to be used with an IndexingSession, so implementations should make sure that their derived classes be thread-safe.
